Some migrants who have been able to claim asylum have shared their stories on
the site [Réfugiés
Bienvenue](https://refugiesbienvenue.com/category/temoignages/) [welcome
refugees]. Art classes have also been set up in Paris by the organisation
_[Dessins sans Papiers](https://www.facebook.com/groups/dessinssanspapiers/)_
[Undocumented Drawings], which enable attendees to share their journeys. The
works are displayed in exhibitions or compiled in books.

